messages.message: do we still support guest login? trying to see if we can deprecate dynamic-proxy but seems it is still used for guest login but I don't see a login as guest from ib home page.
the request came here in case you are wondering: https://instabase.slack.com/archives/CCY413CSU/p1679932489330139?thread_ts=1679906844.071409&cid=CCY413CSU
